example_sentence_english: I am looking for a locker for the bathroom.
The key of the locker is here.
I put the book to the locker.
Take the bag from the locker.
The shoes are in the locker.
There is dust on the locker.
It works well with the locker.

example_sentence_english: The doors of the lockers are new.
